window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The battle is won, but the war rages on.</b></p> <p>Alexandra has survived the Republic's kidnapping attempt, and it has only reinforced her conviction. She must build up her forces and create an army vast enough that no one will ever dare to attack again. Or, failing that, an army large enough to eradicate her enemies no matter where they run.</p> <p>Meanwhile, her two noble allies are finding themselves in a delicate position. Their dungeon town, although prosperous, is threatened from all sides. They are forced to make more and more unsavory alliances to stay ahead of their foes.</p> <p>Lurking in the shadows, the mysterious Order that slew Alexandra sets its plans into motionâ€¦</p>"; 
